# Google Sign-In + Drive backup (OAuth 2.0)
# 0. Enable Google Drive API:
#    https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/drive.googleapis.com
# 1. Credentials: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. OAuth consent screen → External → add your Gmail as Test user
#
# 3. OAuth clients (same project):
#
#    ANDROID (bắt buộc cho APK):
#    - Type: Android
#    - Package: com.truongkieu.Serf
#    - SHA-1: keytool -list -v -keystore android/app/debug.keystore ...
#    → EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID
#    - KHÔNG có mục "Authorized redirect URIs" — Google tự nhận redirect native.
#
#    WEB (bắt buộc trong .env, dùng khi đổi token):
#    - Type: Web application
#    - Authorized redirect URIs: để TRỐNG hoặc chỉ thêm (nếu Console bắt buộc):
#        http://localhost
#    - KHÔNG thêm com.googleusercontent.apps... (Console chỉ cho http/https)
#    → EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID
#
# 4. Copy to .env, rebuild: npm run build:apk

EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID=216435075212-v8fqd366u29t1hgcr8j85p0atmqcosmp.apps.googleusercontent.com
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_IOS_CLIENT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_EXPO_CLIENT_ID=
